    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is a museum-grade 2004 Honda S2000 AP2, showcasing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the F22C1 2.2L longitudinal inline-four, delivering a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. The close-ratio 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw shifts, paired with a factory Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal torque biasing. The chassis is reinforced by its signature X-bone frame and a perfectly tuned double-wishbone suspension at all four corners, ensuring neutral handling and high-speed stability. Mechanically pristine with zero aftermarket modifications, this vehicle maintains its original factory compression and valve clearances. A rare opportunity to acquire a legendary roadster in its purest form.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
