    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is an investment-grade vehicle presented in absolute showroom condition. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a multi-layer professional ceramic coating; you will find no rock chips, swirl marks, or parking lot blemishes. The factory alloy wheels are pristine, with zero curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin remains in a 'time-capsule' state\u2014the premium leather is supple and matte, free of the typical shine or bolster wear found in lesser examples. It has been a strictly smoke-free and pet-free environment, retaining that distinct new-car aroma. Every toggle, screen, and sensor operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule exclusively at authorized service centers; a complete binder of service records is included. The engine bay is meticulously clean, and the undercarriage is free of corrosion. This sale includes both original key fobs, the factory window sticker, and the original owner\u2019s manuals. For the buyer seeking perfection without the showroom price tag, this is the definitive choice.",
